---
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 via-white to-gray-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Enhanced Section Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-24 animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-6 mb-8">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-brand rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-brand">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-2xl">À</span>
          </div>
          <div class="h-12 w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-500 via-soul-500 to-accent-500"></div>
          <div class="text-primary-600 font-bold tracking-[0.15em] text-lg uppercase">Propos</div>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8 leading-tight tracking-tight">
          <span data-i18n="about.title" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 via-primary-700 to-gray-900 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Une voix, un parcours,</span>
          <br>
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-500 via-soul-500 to-accent-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent" data-i18n="about.titleAccent">une mission</span>
        </h2>
        
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-6 mt-10">
          <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-500 to-accent-500 rounded-full"></div>
          <div class="text-accent-500 text-3xl animate-pulse">♪</div>
          <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-500 to-soul-500 rounded-full"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
        <!-- Enhanced Image Section -->
        <div class="animate-on-scroll">
          <div class="relative group">
            <!-- Enhanced background decorative elements -->
            <div class="absolute -inset-6 bg-gradient-brand rounded-3xl transform rotate-3 group-hover:rotate-6 transition-transform duration-700 opacity-20"></div>
            <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-soul rounded-3xl transform -rotate-2 group-hover:-rotate-4 transition-transform duration-700 opacity-30"></div>
            <div class="absolute -inset-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-400 to-primary-400 rounded-3xl transform rotate-1 group-hover:rotate-2 transition-transform duration-700 opacity-20"></div>
            
            <!-- Main image container -->
            <div class="relative bg-white rounded-3xl p-6 shadow-2xl group-hover:shadow-brand-lg transition-all duration-700">
              <img 
                src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1105666/pexels-photo-1105666.jpeg" 
                alt="Mr Valentino en concert" 
                class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full h-96 md:h-[28rem] object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
              />
              
              <!-- Enhanced overlay with brand elements -->
              <div class="absolute top-10 left-10 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl px-6 py-4 shadow-xl">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                  <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-cameroon-green rounded-full shadow-sm"></div>
                  <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-cameroon-red rounded-full shadow-sm"></div>
                  <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-cameroon-yellow rounded-full shadow-sm"></div>
                  <span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 ml-3 tracking-wide">CAMEROUN</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="absolute bottom-10 right-10 bg-primary-600/95 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl px-6 py-4 shadow-xl">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                  <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-acadian-blue rounded-full shadow-sm"></div>
                  <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-acadian-white rounded-full shadow-sm"></div>
                  <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-acadian-red rounded-full shadow-sm"></div>
                  <span class="text-sm font-bold text-white ml-3 tracking-wide">ACADIE</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Enhanced Content Section -->
        <div class="space-y-10 animate-on-scroll">
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-light" data-i18n="about.intro">
              Je m'appelle <strong class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-700 to-soul-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-black">Mr Valentino</strong> (Valentino Nguelieu), artiste interprète originaire du Cameroun, actuellement basé au Nouveau-Brunswick, au Canada.
            </p>

            <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-light" data-i18n="about.passion">
              Depuis tout petit, la musique a été pour moi plus qu'une passion — c'est un moyen d'expression, une thérapie, un langage universel.
            </p>

            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-50 via-soul-50 to-accent-50 rounded-3xl p-8 border-l-4 border-accent-500 shadow-lg">
              <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-light" data-i18n="about.achievements">
                En 2024, j'ai eu l'honneur de remporter le concours <em class="text-accent-600 font-bold">CCNB sur scène</em>, puis d'être sacré <em class="text-soul-600 font-bold">Coup de cœur du public</em> au <strong>Gala de la chanson de Caraquet</strong>.
              </p>
            </div>

            <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-light" data-i18n="about.style">
              J'interprète principalement des chansons francophones aux influences blues, soul, et variétés. Mon univers est émotionnel, vibrant, sincère.
            </p>

            <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-light" data-i18n="about.inspiration">
              Je puise mon inspiration chez des artistes comme <strong class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-700 to-soul-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-black">Lara Fabian</strong>, que j'admire profondément. À travers chaque chanson, je cherche à transmettre une émotion vraie.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Enhanced Stats Section -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-16 pt-10">
            <div class="text-center group">
              <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl hover:shadow-brand transition-all duration-500 group-hover:scale-110 border border-gray-100">
                <div class="text-5xl font-black bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-soul-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4">2024</div>
                <div class="text-lg text-gray-600 font-semibold tracking-wide" data-i18n="about.yearOfConsecration">Année de consécration</div>
                <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-500 to-soul-500 mx-auto mt-4 rounded-full"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center group">
              <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl hover:shadow-accent transition-all duration-500 group-hover:scale-110 border border-gray-100">
                <div class="text-5xl font-black bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-600 to-soul-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4">2</div>
                <div class="text-lg text-gray-600 font-semibold tracking-wide" data-i18n="about.awardsWon">Prix remportés</div>
                <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-500 to-soul-500 mx-auto mt-4 rounded-full"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Enhanced Musical Influences -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 flex items-center">
              <span class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-music rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mr-4 shadow-lg">
                <span class="text-white text-xl">♪</span>
              </span>
              Influences musicales
            </h3>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
              <span class="px-6 py-3 bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-lg font-bold hover:bg-primary-200 transition-colors cursor-default">Blues</span>
              <span class="px-6 py-3 bg-soul-100 text-soul-700 rounded-full text-lg font-bold hover:bg-soul-200 transition-colors cursor-default">Soul</span>
              <span class="px-6 py-3 bg-accent-100 text-accent-700 rounded-full text-lg font-bold hover:bg-accent-200 transition-colors cursor-default">Variétés</span>
              <span class="px-6 py-3 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-lg font-bold hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors cursor-default">Francophone</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>